  "texts": [
    "Smart contracts are written in the form of code.",
    "The written code is sent to the blockchain. 2.",
    "When an event presented in the contract is triggered, the code causes the event to occur.3.",
    "Regulators have the power to scrutinize contract activity on the blockchain.In Bitcoin, the terms and conditions of a successful transaction, double spending verification, and the creation and consumption of new coins are expressed using a straightforward stack language.",
    "As a result, it is crucial that the smart contracts that are deployed are precise and behave decisively."
  ]
